      code: 
        pre:
          - '#'
          - 
            en-us: produce domain predictions with HMMER3 (provides hmmscan) with weak filters.
            es-mx: produzca predicciones de dominios con HMMER3 (provée hmmscan) con filtros débiles.
          - "\n"
          - '#'
          - 
            en-us: this is the slowest step
